channel.title: Annoying problem
channel.description:
Does anyone know how to get rid of this thing...
I'm using a popular 508 as a base for my server, but I cannot get rid of the guys website and name, that is on the actual playing window.... I know people make these as an Anti-Leech, but it's kinda annoying when your advertising your site on a base server, that other people plan to use.
For those of you, who do not kno what I'm talking about, it's David's Davidscape source.
Thanks, Bode
